The paper discusses the use of deep learning computer vision systems for analyzing user interfaces and generating inferences, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the development of automated systems, which could be related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the focus on user interfaces suggests a potential connection to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
